name: VentureRate
tag_list: startup, idea, venture, entrepreneur, community, share
overview:
VentureRate is a place to share your startup ideas and rate others’.

Users submit their business ideas and we help them out by posting feedback. The aim is to build a community that helps entrepreneurs succeed. You can help out by posting your thoughts on submitted ideas and rating them up/down. If you’d like to share you startup, all you have to do is register. Anyone can leave a comment!

Lastly, investors (VCs, Angels, etc) are burdened with more startup pitches than they can deal with. A large portion of these are not very well refined. VentureRate is a place to help you perfect your pitch and get feedback. Our top rated submissions will be presented to VCs.
